      <bioghist id="aspace_28ffd4a9751fca87832868d4ef2750ee">
         <head>Rachel Field, 1894-1942</head>
         <p>Rachel Field, American novelist, poet, and author of children's fiction.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_133492d5d4cff45030508b475370843d">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of letters from Rachel Field to Ruth Stanley-Brown Feis and from Field to Prentiss Taylor. Also included in the collection are writings by Field, many with illustrations by Taylor, and original writings and drawings by Taylor.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_9f1f4160ed26ce3e7491c71447de46b6">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into two series: I. Correspondence, 1917-1942. II. Writings and Drawings, 1928-1933.</p>  
      </arrangement>
